<date notBefore="988" notAfter="989">端拱</date>初<pc>，</pc>籍田<pc>，</pc>封蕭國公<pc>。</pc>俄俶薨<pc>，</pc>起複<pc>，</pc>加兼中書令<pc>。</pc>
